739
00:55:20,239 --> 00:55:22,710
Aku menghabiskan semua energiku dari sosis itu.

740
00:55:24,710 --> 00:55:26,380
Tidak. Maafkan aku.

741
00:55:26,380 --> 00:55:28,779
- Hei!
- Maaf!

742
00:55:28,779 --> 00:55:31,390
Hei! Dasar bedebah tidak loyal.

743
00:55:31,390 --> 00:55:34,759
Ayo. Kita harus pergi.

744
00:55:45,870 --> 00:55:49,670
Hai, Tuan-tuan. Terima kasih atas kerja keras kalian.

745
00:55:50,940 --> 00:55:54,110
Begini, aku

746
00:55:54,980 --> 00:55:56,910
